author: veithen
msg: * Make sure that the InputSource objects returned by ResourceMap have their systemId set as Axis2 relies on this. The generated system IDs are of the form "synapse-reg:///<key>". This fixes SYNAPSE-362.
* Added a unit test for WSDL/XSD import resolution with ResourceMap. This is a unit test for the improvement in SYNAPSE-200 and a regression test for issue SYNAPSE-362.
